Abby Rakic-Platt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abby_Rakic-Platt 0 Abby Rakic-Platt (born 3 May 1993) is a British actress best known for her performances in the television series The Story of Tracy Beaker on the children's channel CBBC as Jackie Hopper. She appeared in a 2010 Sainsbury's Christmas advert.
